  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/0335cf0dcce8ef716042a2e4ba648e3d.avif?t=1742545418\" width=508 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"You always hear about this happening, but never expect it to happen to you\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'TraumaCore Violence' is a 2D Action Game starring \"Uzi\",  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a girl who has just receded into the depths of her psyche.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//COMBAT: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/c81da7522a2ea2fb11fbff37b8d5e977.poster.avif?t=1742545418\" width=420 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/c81da7522a2ea2fb11fbff37b8d5e977.webm?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/c81da7522a2ea2fb11fbff37b8d5e977.mp4?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat is done through crazy high flying combos with an in-depth input and animation cancelling system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Almost all attacks are frame-1-startup leading to a particularly snappy and fast paced combat feel, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >allowing you pull off to insane chains and combos once you master your moveset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//MOVEMENT: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/ac6224081f6a7e7907bd940032d5a152.poster.avif?t=1742545418\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/ac6224081f6a7e7907bd940032d5a152.webm?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/ac6224081f6a7e7907bd940032d5a152.mp4?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your attacks aren't just attacks, each move can alter or add to your momentum,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >allowing for insane speed once you understand how every move works and effects your speed/direction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//COMBO SYSTEM: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every kill, a combo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kills will increase your combo meter, keep a combo going until the end of the level and you will receive a massive point bonus,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or cash-out your combo for its weight in health, whichever you feel matters most.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//FULL CAMPAIGN CO-OP: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At any time, you can go into the game options to enable a fully functional 2-player co-op mode, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >take on your problems with a (imaginary) friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(This requires two controllers to be connected)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//STORY&VISUALS: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uzi is trapped within her own psyche, plunged into the depths of her own mind trying to figure out how to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The atmosphere and visual style intentionally pulls from a style coined \"TraumaCore\",</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >in which heavily edited stock and/or familiar images and/or art are used to fuel a sense of overwhelming stress and dread.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/0335cf0dcce8ef716042a2e4ba648e3d.avif?t=1742545418\" width=508 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"You always hear about this happening, but never expect it to happen to you\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'TraumaCore Violence' is a 2D Action Game starring \"Uzi\",  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a girl who has just receded into the depths of her psyche.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//COMBAT: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/c81da7522a2ea2fb11fbff37b8d5e977.poster.avif?t=1742545418\" width=420 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/c81da7522a2ea2fb11fbff37b8d5e977.webm?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/c81da7522a2ea2fb11fbff37b8d5e977.mp4?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat is done through crazy high flying combos with an in-depth input and animation cancelling system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Almost all attacks are frame-1-startup leading to a particularly snappy and fast paced combat feel, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >allowing you pull off to insane chains and combos once you master your moveset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//MOVEMENT: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/ac6224081f6a7e7907bd940032d5a152.poster.avif?t=1742545418\" width=420 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/ac6224081f6a7e7907bd940032d5a152.webm?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284460/extras/ac6224081f6a7e7907bd940032d5a152.mp4?t=1742545418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your attacks aren't just attacks, each move can alter or add to your momentum,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >allowing for insane speed once you understand how every move works and effects your speed/direction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//COMBO SYSTEM: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every kill, a combo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kills will increase your combo meter, keep a combo going until the end of the level and you will receive a massive point bonus,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or cash-out your combo for its weight in health, whichever you feel matters most.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//FULL CAMPAIGN CO-OP: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At any time, you can go into the game options to enable a fully functional 2-player co-op mode, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >take on your problems with a (imaginary) friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(This requires two controllers to be connected)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >//STORY&VISUALS: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uzi is trapped within her own psyche, plunged into the depths of her own mind trying to figure out how to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The atmosphere and visual style intentionally pulls from a style coined \"TraumaCore\",</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >in which heavily edited stock and/or familiar images and/or art are used to fuel a sense of overwhelming stress and dread.</p>",
